    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/4ec01933e6257bd5327d60dae8b7a34e.avif?t=1727294114\" width=800 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/fb122c72d8c90ac5c2cd9ac3b87f1376.poster.avif?t=1727294114\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/fb122c72d8c90ac5c2cd9ac3b87f1376.webm?t=1727294114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/fb122c72d8c90ac5c2cd9ac3b87f1376.mp4?t=1727294114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doomtide is a turn-based RPG with city-builder elements set in a flooded world of monsters and ancient horrors. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Venture Forth Across the Dark Seas</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct an island town, gather resources, and find ancient dark artefacts to strengthen your hold on the seas. Recruit heroes with their own unique skills, abilities, and equipment and put them to the test in an ever expanding ocean of adventures. Test your mettle in classic turn-based combat within ever more complex dungeon delves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/f7476aeda1872027963e478fa7e6ddff.poster.avif?t=1727294114\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/f7476aeda1872027963e478fa7e6ddff.webm?t=1727294114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/f7476aeda1872027963e478fa7e6ddff.mp4?t=1727294114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique monochrome aesthetic and atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of unique RPG heroes to collect, upgrade, and upskill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create, improve, decorate, and enhance your island to better serve you and the Dark Gods</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pursue paths of glory, power, and knowledge as you set your own goals and fail states throughout gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark and foreboding narrative across a procedurally-generated sea of islands and stories to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/6118fd972d9d947ced46a812fda118c9.poster.avif?t=1727294114\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/6118fd972d9d947ced46a812fda118c9.webm?t=1727294114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/6118fd972d9d947ced46a812fda118c9.mp4?t=1727294114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>How far are you willing to go to accomplish your goals?</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237110/extras/84a4bd63974fd596bc66eba8e467865c.avif?t=1727294114\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p>",
